{"tid":2318300,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共產黨回應美國：我無搞鳩你自由世界 做乜搞我 ? 同我入廁所傾傾佢","createTime":"2020-12-09T08:46:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T03:44:54.000Z","uid":21470,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b29777a45e7ac6aa2542f178bf5a07fecc013c23","tid":2318300,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T08:46:33.000Z","msg":"外交部：將堅決反制美國制裁 絕不吞下損害主權苦果<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人趙立堅表示，中方針對美國制裁全國人大全體副委員長的惡劣行徑，將堅決有力反制，中方絕不會吞下損害中國主權、安全及發展利益的苦果。<br />\n<br />\n趙立堅又回應美國國務卿蓬佩奧指，美國對華政策是不可逆轉，重申中美關係之所以呈現建交以來最嚴峻的局面，根本原因在於美方一些人固守陳舊的冷戰思維，以及意識形態偏見，從零和博弈角度看待中國及中美關系，當務之急是雙方一同努力，排除各種干擾阻力，實現中美關係平穩過渡，爭取下一階段的中美關係重啟對話，重回正軌，重建互信。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china/2369966\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2369966&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUEbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=14e80bc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2369966</a>"},{"pid":"ae4665516f3bbd8f5de086c04571c88860da4f34","tid":2318300,"uid":48362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T08:47:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a74c3c4c833d284b6b56bcad1d425eef1c32d7","tid":2318300,"uid":122773,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T08:49:19.000Z","msg":"收嗲啦 唔係認低威丫 天朝大國 放2粒原子彈去洋鬼子到 DLLM <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fb31e3cfaff343b85b5a827032b